{"tid":1136314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年年薪3.67億 或交稅5000萬 騰訊總裁劉熾平勢成新「打工皇帝」","createTime":"2019-05-03T02:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T05:39:43.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9b3867d5cfab7048bc75ebfee3989c1e486181","tid":1136314,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA3-67%E5%84%84-%E6%88%96%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%855000%E8%90%AC-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%8A%89%E7%86%BE%E5%B9%B3%E5%8B%A2%E6%88%90%E6%96%B0-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%9D-214500601.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA3-67%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A8%25855000%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%258A%2589%25E7%2586%25BE%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258B%25A2%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2587%25E5%25B8%259D-214500601.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=430ba825\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA3-67%E5%84%84-%E6%88%96%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%855000%E8%90%AC-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%8A%89%E7%86%BE%E5%B9%B3%E5%8B%A2%E6%88%90%E6%96%B0-%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%87%E5%B8%9D-214500601.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uWUbBdMGcAElb6tmKPFZVA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/a774c795f08176e7f2ab021cd95d7e94\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuWUbBdMGcAElb6tmKPFZVA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fa774c795f08176e7f2ab021cd95d7e94&h=694744fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉熾平<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全港交稅最多的「打工皇帝」花落誰家？蟬聯多年、向來有「香港打工皇帝」之稱的長和集團聯席董事總經理霍建寧，雖然每年年薪數以億元計，但一山還有一山高，有機會被他人奪去「打工皇帝」寶座。騰訊執行董事兼總裁劉熾平去年年薪達三億一千三百萬元人民幣（即三億六千七百萬港元），按年增加三成二，隨時需要交稅五千萬元，或成為交稅最多的「新打工皇帝」。<br />\n<br />\n霍建寧料繳稅3390萬<br />\n<br />\n「億萬打工皇帝」霍建寧雖然已被人趕上，但據長和年報顯示，收入之多亦令不少人羨慕，霍去年總酬金增加百分之七點五，至二億二千六百萬元，當中二億一千三百萬元屬酌情花紅。撇除免稅額及其他稅務計劃，預料霍建寧於二○一八/一九年度要繳的薪俸稅約三千三百九十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n年薪逾千萬增至3000人<br />\n<br />\n稅務局自數年前起，已不再公布單宗最高薪俸稅繳稅額，稅務局局長黃權輝指是按法例要求保密，因為公布該數字變相可以按個別人士公布的年薪推算出身份，而且由於課稅調整等，有關坊間推算亦不準確，故不再公布，故上述數字是按公司報告數值推算。<br />\n<br />\n稅局資料顯示，在一七/一八年度，年薪逾千萬元的「高薪族」有三千人，人數增幅逾兩成，佔整體薪俸稅納稅人約百分之零點一，共繳納一百億元薪俸稅，每人平均繳稅三百三十六萬元，以標準稅率百分之十五計算，該批打工皇帝每人平均年薪達二千二百三十八萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatfat啦"},{"pid":"48ad58a7a55f0a07742896ee970cf6f18194f616","tid":1136314,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/569449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/569449/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n入面呢度好多人表演「交稅供獻香港」神功<br />\n唔知佢地份稅佔劉總, 霍總果份幾千份之幾呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7055b4fc76490a8d0aa8beea96e160b23f60cd57","tid":1136314,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3f3ad222f71177c539539211a9754de36180047","tid":1136314,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"開間公司黎出糧，唔知最後比幾錢稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7fec6321383c341ca3efc7f0305274c80235ce","tid":1136314,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"交稅仲多過我成世人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b2d0398a90ce03026f1879a9900870210cdde","tid":1136314,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c7fec6321383c341ca3efc7f0305274c80235ce","tid":1136314,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"交稅仲多過我成世人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"不要說了.JPG"},{"pid":"e3173a4bedebb9dced0acd937b59f72593858d4e","tid":1136314,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"香港好似試過有人交2億稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f33f71f675fac1de51daf2b223d8b025b3141f7","tid":1136314,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"唔知佢交齊稅未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca7f8ff163a005ef3baccf0a25026ce41468ae7","tid":1136314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解交稅俾香港稅局？<br />\n唔係大陸稅局？"},{"pid":"a8e5c41fc8f0bf2906a04f3f432f1667dc682e4a","tid":1136314,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"Director fee"}]}